# Build context is the monorepo ROOT (see apps/server/Dockerfile), so the
# ignore rules that matter live here, not in apps/server/.dockerignore.
# Critically, never bake local .env secrets into the image — env is
# injected at runtime via Railway service variables.
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
.turbo
**/.turbo
.git
*.log
apps/web/dist
.data
**/.data
